import React from 'react'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import NavDropdown from 'react-bootstrap/NavDropdown';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';

function Navigation() {
  return (
    <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Brand href="#home">ICCR</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
          <Nav className="me-auto">
            <Nav.Link href="/">Home</Nav.Link>
            <NavDropdown title="Regional Offices" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a1">Ahmedabad</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a2">
                Bangalore
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a3">Bhopal</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a4">
                Bhubaneswar
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a5">Chennai</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a6">
                Delhi University
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a7">Goa</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a8">
                Guwahati
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a9">Hyderabad</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a10">
                Jammu
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a11">Kolkata</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a12">
                Lucknow
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a13">Mumbai</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a14">
                Patna
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a15">Pune</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a16">
                Shillong
              </NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a17">Thiruvananthapuram</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#a18">
                Varanasi
              </NavDropdown.Item>
            </NavDropdown>
            <Nav.Link href="#sup">Support</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="#contact">Contact us</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="project/add">Add Regional Office</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="/addevent">Add Event</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link href="/login">Login</Nav.Link>
          </Nav>
          <Form className="d-flex">
            <Form.Control
              type="search"
              placeholder="Search"
              className="me-2"
              aria-label="Search"
            />
            <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
          </Form>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
}

export default Navigation;
